Name: E-Startup
About the game: About E-Startup Manage, develop and build the startup of your dreams! Go public with your company and invest, designing your own rooms and products in detail! Perform contracts to grow and maintain your popularity. Develop your own social media and streaming platform, expand and win users! Oops! Out of money? No problem, the bank will lend you a little - But be careful! The International Bank is not to be trifled with. Become a successful startup entrepreneur, your own way. Features Fleshed-out construction mode With our sophisticated, easy-to-use construction mode, you can design your own rooms the way you like them. Realistic stock exchange simulation Invest in the stock market and become big! Orders and merchandise Process orders and produce merchandise with the help of materials bought online. Manage your team You can hire your workers according to motivation and skills. Dissatisfied? You can fire them or send them on vacation.
